description: When I post on Facebook, Twitter or even here, I get comments from people asking me “when are you gonna make some new videos?” So apparently many of my subscribers are not getting notifications. Nothing new there, but in case you haven’t seen my 3 latest videos, head over to ODD TV to check them out. I recently changed my channel name back to ODD TV, so it’s not ODD Reality anymore. Much love everyone.
